  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they have exhibits, the pictures, some of the torturers, and they have a movie which they show in the museum which is in the old prison area itself.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the outside is no longer open to the public, just the-- where the prison area was is-- is open to the public.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- well, the crematoriums are still there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're just outside of the prison area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you can go through the crematoriums and the other buildings that were used to pile on the dead people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then the museum itself is maintained by the German government at this time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] A number of my men have been back there are also, men that I served with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On two occasions, we took-- we took members of our regimental association and their wives.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At the time, I was by myself, but my wife has been there twice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we have visited Germany at least five times in our travels of Europe and we've been to most of the European countries, except the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --part that was under Russian domination.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We've never been to any of those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My last visit to Dachau was just three years ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a group here headed by a lieutenant governor, a small group of people, wanted to explore-- we were having a problem with neo-Nazis here in this country, as you know, and people who put out false propaganda.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a small group of us headed by our lieutenant governor and several Jewish people, also one Arabic type, Japanese, Chinese, we had an ethnic mix.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We wanted to explore what the German government was doing about their neo-Nazi movement.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
